nodes.text: A rebel group fought against the Galactic Empire sometime during or before the year 1 BBY. notes  Although for a while the rebels had the upper hand in the battle, Imperial dropships soon came to assist the Imperial forces.

The rebel group was first mentioned in the "Imperial dropship" entry in the in-game databank of the PlayStation 3/Xbox 360 versions of the LucasArts video game Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II, which was released in 2010.
